'''詹姆斯·M·坎托'''（James M. Cantor，{{bd|1966年|1月2日|||catIdx=C}}），加拿大[[臨床心理學|臨床心理學家]]、[[性學|性學家]]。他在研究[[性慾亢進|性慾亢進]]和非典型的性興趣方面挺有建樹，是[[性偏離|性偏離]]的專家<ref name="toronto">{{cite web |title=Dr. James M. Cantor - Department of Psychiatry |url=http://www.psychiatry.utoronto.ca/people/dr-james-m-cantor/ |publisher=University of Toronto |accessdate=2018-06-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914215523/http://www.psychiatry.utoronto.ca/people/dr-james-m-cantor/ |archivedate=2017-09-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他曾任《性虐待》期刊的編輯<ref>{{cite web |first=Sarah |last=Kaplan |authorlink=Sarah Kaplan |title=The Jared Fogle case: Why we understand so little about child sex abuse |work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |date=2015-08-20 |accessdate=2016-07-07 |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/08/20/why-we-understand-so-little-about-pedophilia-and-sex-crimes-against-children/ |archive-date=2015-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820231606/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/08/20/why-we-understand-so-little-about-pedophilia-and-sex-crimes-against-children/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並對[[恋童|恋童]]者進行了腦部[[神经科学|神經研究]]，有關結果被視為為戀童與生俱來、不可改變的說法提供了證據<ref>{{cite web |first=Jennifer |last=Bleyer |title=How can we stop pedophiles |publisher=Slate |date=2012-09-24 |accessdate=2012-12-02 |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2012/09/stop_childhood_sexual_abuse_how_to_treat_pedophilia_.2.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104191821/http://www.slate.com/articles/health_and_science/medical_examiner/2012/09/stop_childhood_sexual_abuse_how_to_treat_pedophilia_.2.html |archive-date=2018-01-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、

坎托為多倫多大學精神醫學部的助理教授、{{link-en|成癮與精神健康中心|Centre for Addiction and Mental Health}}法律和心理健康研究部部長<ref name=Cantorhome>{{cite web |url=http://individual.utoronto.ca/james_cantor/ |title=Dr. James Cantor |publisher=University of Toronto Faculty of Medicine |accessdate=2010-08-23 |archive-date=2019-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216150849/http://individual.utoronto.ca/james_cantor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；《{{link-en|性侵略期刊|Journal of Sexual Aggression}}》、《[[性研究期刊|性研究期刊]]》、《[[性行為檔案|性行為檔案]]》的[[編輯委員會|編輯委員會]]委員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.atsa.com/pubJrnl.html |title=Publications: ATSA Journal |publisher=Association for the Treatment of Sexual Abusers |accessdate=2010-08-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707183740/http://www.atsa.com/pubJrnl.html |archivedate=2011-07-07 |dead-url=yes }}
