坎托跟{{link-en|雷·布兰查德|Ray Blanchard}}合著了一篇論文，其於2008年發表。當中建議[[DSM-5|DSM-5]]把戀童更改成[[戀少年|戀童-戀少年障礙]]<ref name=phd/>；把戀少年定為一種[[精神疾患|疾病]]，同時把它分為三個子類型：戀童（認為少於11歲的孩童有性吸引力）、戀少年（認為11-14歲的孩童有性吸引力）、戀童-戀少年（認為兩個年齡組別皆有性吸引力）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/DSM-V+work+on+paraphilias+begins+in+earnest-a0215844762 |author=Frieden, Joyce |title=DSM-V work on paraphilias begins in earnest. |work=Clinical Psychiatry News |date=2009-12-01 |accessdate=2012-04-24 |archive-date=2020-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220164233/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/DSM-V+work+on+paraphilias+begins+in+earnest-a0215844762 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這篇論文主要認為DSM-IV-TR對戀童的定義不足以涵蓋所有認為「未發育完全者」擁有性吸引力的人<ref name=phd>{{cite journal |author1=Blanchard, Ray |author2=Cantor, James M. |year=2008 |title=Pedophilia, Hebephilia, and the ''DSM-V'' |journal=Archives of Sexual Behavior |volume=38 |issue=3 |pages=335–350 |doi=10.1007/s10508-008-9399-9  |last3=Wherrett |last4=Kuban |last5=Cantor |last6=Blak |last7=Dickey |last8=Klassen |pmid=18686026}}</ref>。此一提議受到了理查德·格林（Richard Green）和卡伦·富兰克林（Karen Franklin）的批評，認為他們為了迎合社會的道德法律標準，把促使人類繁殖下一代的行為病理化<ref>{{cite journal |author=Green, Richard |year=2010 |title=Sexual Preference for 14-Year-Olds as a Mental Disorder: You Can't Be Serious!! |journal=Archives of Sexual Behavior |volume=39 |issue=3 |pages=585–586 |pmid=20204488 |doi=10.1007/s10508-010-9602-7}}</ref><ref name="franklin">{{Cite journal |doi=10.1002/bsl.934 |title=Hebephilia: Quintessence of diagnostic pretextuality |year=2010 |last1=Franklin |first1=K. |journal=Behavioral Sciences & the Law |volume=28 |issue=6 |pages=751–768 |pmid=21110392 }}</ref>。坎托等人的提議最終不為DSM-5採納。

